      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i know i should probably see a doctor but it feels less like a medical thing and more like they're actually doing it on purpose. like the hum only happens when the neighbors are home and it feels so targeted. have you heard anything about people using subsonic frequencies or infrasound for mood control? i feel like it makes too much sense for why i suddenly feel so on edge.",
